Customised software (also known as bespoke software or tailor-made software) is software that is specially developed for some specific organization or other user.

Technology
Consulting

Technology consulting is the process of advising businesses on how to best use technology and software to benefit their business. It can refer to the design and development of new technology etc.

Business Analytics is the process by which businesses use statistical methods and technologies for analyzing historical data in order to gain new insight and improve strategic decision-making.
